      "content": "but it's not just a bad night. it's been like this every single day. i look at the door and i don't even want to walk through it. i'm just so tired of pretending that things will get better when they clearly won't. it feels like i'm just dragging this broken version of myself around for no reason. wouldn't it be easier if i just wasn't here to have to deal with it all?",
